summary: Preset inspired in australian singer Lenka
descriptionHtml:
My first contribution to the site. A RaceMenu Preset inspired by australian singer Lenka.

This is just a preset, that means that you need other mods to use it.

[size=3][b]Requirements:[/b][/size] (If you want her to look like the pictures)
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/29624/?]RaceMenu [/url]by expired6978
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/35327/?]SG Female Eyebrows[/url] by hellosanta
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/68311/?]KS Hairdos[/url] [size=2]by Kalilies, Stealthic Khaos and Shocky[/size]
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/73512/?]Leyenda Skin[/url] by HeroedeLeyenda


You can make a follower of this preset if you want, you have full permission.
